AI Tools Workshop for Fresher Graduates
Build, Automate & Deploy AI-Powered Products — From Idea to Launch

Phase 1: Idea Generation – “Think Like an AI Innovator”
Goal: Transform your raw ideas into real-world AI product concepts.
Tools: GPT-5 | Perplexity | Grok AI | Gemini | Copilot
Learn:
How to brainstorm startup-level ideas with AI.
Draft problem statements and market-fit insights.
Use AI for competitor analysis and feature planning.
Outcome: A validated, AI-generated project idea with clear goals and feature scope.

Phase 2: Interface Design – “Design Smarter, Not Harder”
Goal: Convert your idea into a working UI prototype.
Tools: Uizard | Google Stitch | Relume.io | Figma AI
Learn:
Create mobile & web layouts using AI-based design tools.
Generate wireframes, user flows, and style guides automatically.
Collaborate in real time for design feedback.
Outcome: A complete, responsive app prototype ready for feature integration.

Phase 3: Feature Building – “Code with AI Co-Developers”
Goal: Turn your prototype into a functional application.
Tools: Lovable AI | Replit AI | Bolt.new | Emergent AI | Rork AI
Learn:
Auto-generate front-end & back-end code using AI assistance.
Integrate APIs, data, and real logic.
Debug and enhance code using conversational AI support.
Outcome: A working MVP (Minimum Viable Product) created through AI-assisted coding.

Phase 4: Testing & Automation – “Automate Smarter Workflows”
Goal: Test, improve, and automate your product lifecycle.
Tools: Make.com | Claude | Zapier | Claude Code | Supabase
Learn:
Automate testing, data flow, and backend workflows.
Connect app components using no-code integrations.
Use AI to review, optimize, and document your system.
Outcome: A tested, automated system ready for real-world deployment.

Phase 5: Live Deployment – “Launch Like a Pro”
Goal: Publish your AI product and make it accessible to users.
Tools: Vercel | Netlify | Flowise | GitHub Copilot
Learn:
Deploy full-stack web apps instantly.
Use GitHub Copilot for CI/CD integration.
Host AI workflows visually with Flowise.
Outcome: Your project goes live — shareable link, working app, and deployment confidence.
Final Outcome for Participants

By the end of this workshop, every participant will:
✅ Conceptualize an AI-based project idea
✅ Design and prototype an interactive UI
✅ Build and automate product features with AI
✅ Test and deploy their app live
✅ Showcase a professional portfolio project built with 15+ AI tools
